<blockquote>
  <p>💻 <a href="https://github.com/facebookresearch/dinov3" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">GitHub</a> | 🤗 <a href="https://huggingface.co/facebook" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">HuggingFace</a></p>
